            <thetext>For making it possible to react to momentum on iOS device, qx.Mobile should fire a momentumStart/momentumEnd event.

This is very useful because iOS does not fire any scroll events as long as momentum scroll is active.
With this feature, you can at least react to the start and finish of the momentum animation, and keep the UI consistent.</thetext>
